Ball in the Hole  -  Game Description
---------------------------------------------------

This Open Source mini-game consist in a scene where you control a ball, the main character, and you can move all arround the scene.
In this scene there are several panels that add points to the player everytime the ball step on them.
There are another panels that have special features. One increment/decrement the amount of points that panels can add to the player.
Other are fragile panels that can crash and set a hole in the scene. If the ball goes through a hole it falls on it and the game is over.
There is a growing panel, which is a fragile one, but it grows with every step of the ball.
